## BabyELF Revenge
---
### Description
A [BabyELF](https://0x00sec.org/t/crackme-babyelf/7268) sequel since @0x00pf and @Leeky nailed it in no time (I hope this one cannot be solved the same way :sweat_smile:).
--- ### Rules
* Make the binary display _Congrats!_ * Patch more than **4 bits** and you’re disqualified. **Don’t patch any instruction!**
